Serves.

Qty.
_ tomatoes.
_ onions.
_ chilies.

Same as sambar, except for frying, add only onion (very big, add one half, very small, add one, etc) and (2 spoon of ginger garlic paste). 
Chili chunks, not in blender
One tomato

Instructions.
1. Pour a medium amount of oil to cover bottom of bowl. Add mustard
   seeds.

2. When oil is hot enough/when mustard seeds have begun to pop, then
   add the onions.
